{"tid":1460263,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[G20]重點必提的元朗黑夜，國外對武警暴力可受度高","createTime":"2019-08-13T02:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T02:16:37.000Z","uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f357d48b3bec9d2ebc04f9d6b201211ef9be13b1","tid":1460263,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:10:24.000Z","msg":"每個國家的文化都不同，民眾對武警的暴力可容忍程度都各有不同。<br />\n例如美國因民眾可持槍，則使武警武力有過火，大家都可以接受，而且他們都習以為常<br />\n反而元朗黑夜係所有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文明</span></strong>國家跟民眾都不能接受。<br />\n希望G20團隊可以聽到並考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8f112d745de2dd850fd07f0538a71d2cb892cb","tid":1460263,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"20"},{"pid":"ff1055bafa7cac33622f986e10cd71893148e310","tid":1460263,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"19"},{"pid":"cdf2bf3a636ff2c8db40208c2b2ca7ef86e43073","tid":1460263,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:13:29.000Z","msg":"18"},{"pid":"6bf246eee974536fe72442bac32fa5b80277606e","tid":1460263,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:13:39.000Z","msg":"17"},{"pid":"aa85c7fabbe874b5b33fe35da30817a86ae28d0e","tid":1460263,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:13:50.000Z","msg":"16"},{"pid":"098cd4576e38f072936348b83e2cddf8ffe4e9ef","tid":1460263,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:14:00.000Z","msg":"15"},{"pid":"48318c6d72e2baac0bbec15e3b87ce36b0b6c601","tid":1460263,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"14"},{"pid":"74b91c8116f478a03ca5893961a5075dea7da148","tid":1460263,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:14:24.000Z","msg":"13"},